Plotting Transformed Variables

Which variables are statistically different between the untransformed data?

Below will employ a two sample t test to test if the populations are equal for each variable. We assume unequal variances despite the power transformation as the IQR spread is not equal in all cases. We will also run a Moods Median test to test for differences in median rather than mean.
